Title: Magdalene 26 (2)
Plot: After the shooting in the hospital in which Stella is wounded the involvement of the priest becomes clear. With the shooter killed there is no chance for interrogation, but his body provides a useful clue linking back to the cold case. In the meantime things become even more complicated when a women turns up who looks a lot like the one in the hospital.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence, sexual violence & content that may disturb
